author: owenb
msg: Improvement to service caching. Set a limit on the cache size. When the number of entries in the cache nears the limit, the oldest entries in the cache will be purged.
The size of the cache can be set via a feature called WSIF_FEATURE_SERVICE_CACHE_SIZE on the WSIFServiceFactory. The default size is 100.
